00291 static int
00292 ReadBit (Set_Vector vector, int element)
00293 {
00294   int index, select, bit_position;
00295   _32bit value, mask;
00296 
00297   index = ABS (element);
00298   index = Set_INDEX (index);
00299   select = Set_WORD_SELECT (index);
00300   bit_position = Set_BIT_SELECT (index);
00301   value = vector[select];
00302   mask = 1 << bit_position;     /* generate bit mask */
00303   return ((value & mask) != 0);
00304 }
00305 
00306 static int
00307 SetBit (Set_Vector vector, int element)
00308 {
00309   int index, select, bit_position;
00310   _32bit mask;
00311 
00312   index = ABS (element);
00313   index = Set_INDEX (index);
00314   select = Set_WORD_SELECT (index);
00315   bit_position = Set_BIT_SELECT (index);
00316   mask = (1 << bit_position);
00317   return (vector[select] |= mask);
00318 }

00320 static int
00321 ClearBit (Set_Vector vector, int element)
00322 {
00323   int index, select, bit_position;
00324   _32bit mask;
00325 
00326   index = ABS (element);
00327   index = Set_INDEX (index);
00328   select = Set_WORD_SELECT (index);
00329   bit_position = Set_BIT_SELECT (index);
00330   mask = ~(1 << bit_position);
00331   return (vector[select] &= mask);
00332 }

00336 Set_in (Set set, int element)
00337 {
00338   int sign, base, max_base;
00339   Set_Vector *vectors;
00340 
00341   if (set == 0)
00342     return 0;
00343

00358 int
00359 Set_size (Set set)
00360 {
00361   int i, b, b1, b2, b3, b4, b5, b6, b7, b8;
00362   Set_Vector *varray;
00363 
00364   if (set == 0)                 /* empty set */
00365     return 0;
00366 
00367   b1 = b2 = b3 = b4 = b5 = b6 = b7 = b8 = 0;
00368   for (b = 0; b < 2; b++)
00369     {
00370       varray = set->varray[b];
00371       for (i = 0; i < set->max_base[b]; i++)
00372         {
00373           Set_Vector vc;
00374 #ifdef POPCNT
00375           int t1, t2, t3, t4, t5, t6, t7, t8;
00376 #else
00377           int j;
00378           _32bit mask;
00379 #endif
00380 
00381           if (!(vc = varray[i]))
00382             continue;
00383 
00384 #ifdef POPCNT
00385           POPCNT (t1, vc[0]);
00386           POPCNT (t2, vc[1]);
00387           POPCNT (t3, vc[2]);
00388           POPCNT (t4, vc[3]);
00389           POPCNT (t5, vc[4]);
00390           POPCNT (t6, vc[5]);
00391           POPCNT (t7, vc[6]);
00392           POPCNT (t8, vc[7]);
00393           
00394           b1 += t1;
00395           b2 += t2;
00396           b3 += t3;
00397           b4 += t4;
00398           b5 += t5;
00399           b6 += t6;
00400           b7 += t7;
00401           b8 += t8;
00402 #else
00403           mask = 1;
00404 
00405           for (j = 0; j < 32; j++)
00406             {                   /* for each bit */
00407               b1 += ((vc[0] & mask) != 0);
00408               b2 += ((vc[1] & mask) != 0);
00409               b3 += ((vc[2] & mask) != 0);
00410               b4 += ((vc[3] & mask) != 0);
00411               b5 += ((vc[4] & mask) != 0);
00412               b6 += ((vc[5] & mask) != 0);
00413               b7 += ((vc[6] & mask) != 0);
00414               b8 += ((vc[7] & mask) != 0);
00415               mask = mask << 1;
00416             }
00417 #endif
00418         }
00419     }
00420 
00421   return (((b1 + b2) + (b3 + b4)) + ((b5 + b6) + (b7 + b8)));
00422 }
